OL,3,CJames Watson: Nobel prize winner and
OL,4,Cdouble-helix DNA pioneer dies aged 97
OL,6,FHe also helped guide efforts to map
OL,7,Fthe human genome. But he was widely
OL,8,Fcondemned for racist remarks later on
OL,9,Fand left his job as chancellor of the
OL,10,Fprestigious Cold Spring Harbour
OL,11,FLaboratory in New York.
OL,13,FHe was also stripped of his honorary
OL,14,Ftitles in 2019 after repeated comments
OL,15,Fabout race and intelligence, making
OL,16,Freference to a view that genes cause a
OL,17,Fdifference on average IQ tests between
OL,18,Fblack and white people.
