OL,3,CJames Watson: Nobel prize winner and
OL,4,Cdouble-helix DNA pioneer dies aged 97
OL,6,FWatson shared the Nobel Prize with
OL,7,Fcollaborator Francis Crick and
OL,8,Fscientist Maurice Wilkins for
OL,9,Fdiscovering in 1953 that DNA was
OL,10,Fshaped like a long, gently twisting
OL,11,Fladder.
OL,13,FKnowing the structure of DNA was key
OL,14,Fto figuring out how the genetic
OL,15,Fmaterial works.
