OL,3,CJames Watson: Nobel prize winner and
OL,4,Cdouble-helix DNA pioneer dies aged 97
OL,6,FThe groundbreaking discovery was a
OL,7,Fhuge advancement in science that gave
OL,8,Fway to the field of molecular biology.
OL,10,FHelping crack the code on how DNA
OL,11,Fstores information and how its special
OL,12,Fstructure allows the molecule to
OL,13,Freplicate itself.
OL,15,FWatson later sold his Nobel Prize gold
OL,16,Fmedal at auction in 2014 for #3.6
OL,17,Fmillion. He later said the sale of the
OL,18,Fmedal came after he was excluded from
OL,19,Fthe scientific community because of
OL,20,Fhis comments on race.
